reviewText: The Breed / Day of the Dead, The Need to Feed (Blu-ray) combo consists of two watchable movies that are not the best of their kinds. The picture and sound quality of both films are fine. Both movies are presented in widescreen.

Been wanting to get day of the dead on blu ray for awhile now,but didn't want the 3d. One bc of the bad reviews,so when I saw this deal for two movies for the price of one,i jumpd on it.good movies of separate disks.great dts 5.1 sound,and the transfer is pretty good to.highly recommend this blu ray
